Privacy Policy
Easy Fast is a fasting tracker app that helps you monitor and manage your intermittent fasting schedule. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your information when you use our Play Store app, Apple Store app, and website (collectively, the “Services”).
What Information Do We Collect?
We collect information that you provide to us when you:
Register for an account
Create or edit your profile
Set your fasting goals and preferences
Log your fasting activities
Interact with other users
Contact us
Otherwise use our Services
This information may include your name, email address, password, age, gender, weight, height, health conditions, fasting history, and other personal details.
We also collect information that is automatically generated when you use our Services, such as your device information, IP address, browser type, operating system, language, location, time zone, app usage, and other technical data. We use cookies and similar technologies to collect and store this information, as well as to provide and improve our Services. You can manage your cookie preferences in your browser settings or in our app settings.
How Do We Use Your Information?
We use your information for the following purposes:
To provide and improve our Services:
Creating and maintaining your account, displaying your fasting progress and statistics, providing personalized feedback and recommendations, enabling social features, and facilitating customer support and technical assistance.
To communicate with you:
Sending you notifications, reminders, updates, newsletters, promotions, surveys, and other information related to our Services or your interests. You can opt out of receiving these communications at any time by following the instructions in the messages or in our app settings.
To protect our Services:
Detecting, preventing, and resolving fraud, security, legal, and technical issues, enforcing our terms and conditions, and complying with our legal obligations and requests from authorities.
To analyze and research our Services:
Measuring and understanding how our Services are used, evaluating and improving our Services, developing new features and services, and conducting market research and user feedback.
How Do We Share Your Information?
We do not sell, rent, or trade your information to any third parties for their own marketing purposes. We may share your information with the following parties for the purposes described above:
Our affiliates and subsidiaries:
Who are subject to this privacy policy or similar policies that protect your information.
Our service providers and partners:
Who help us provide and improve our Services, such as hosting, analytics, advertising, payment, and communication services. These parties are contractually obligated to use your information only in accordance with our instructions and this privacy policy, and to implement appropriate security measures to protect your information.
Other users:
If you choose to share your information or interact with them through our Services, such as posting comments, joining groups, or sending messages. You can control your privacy settings and visibility in our app settings.
The public:
If you choose to share your information or content publicly through our Services, such as posting reviews, ratings, or testimonials. You can delete or edit your public information or content at any time in our app settings.
The law and authorities:
If we are required or permitted to do so by law, regulation, court order, subpoena, warrant, or legal process, or if we believe that it is necessary or appropriate to protect our rights, property, safety, or the safety of others, or to comply with a request from a government or law enforcement agency.
How Do We Protect Your Information?
We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, modification, or destruction, using industry-standard technical and organizational security measures. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information. If you have any questions about the security of your information, please contact us at
info@easyfastapp.com
.
How Long Do We Keep Your Information?
We retain your information for as long as necessary to provide and improve our Services, comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements. When we no longer need your information for these purposes, we will delete or anonymize it in accordance with our data retention policies and applicable laws. You can also request to delete your account and information at any time by contacting us at
info@easyfastapp.com
.
What Are Your Choices and Rights?
You have the following choices and rights regarding your information:
Access, update, correct, or delete your information:
At any time in our app settings or by contacting us at
info@easyfastapp.com
. Please note that some information may remain in our records for legal or technical reasons, or as required by law.
Opt-out of receiving marketing communications:
At any time by following the instructions in the messages or in our app settings. Please note that we may still send you non-marketing communications, such as service-related messages, confirmations, receipts, and updates.
Manage your cookie preferences:
In your browser settings or in our app settings. Please note that disabling or blocking cookies may affect the functionality and performance of our Services.
Withdraw your consent:
To our use of your information at any time by contacting us at
info@easyfastapp.com
. Please note that withdrawing your consent may affect your ability to use some or all of our Services.
Exercise your rights under applicable data protection laws:
Such as the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict, object, or port your information, or to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority, by contacting us at
info@easyfastapp.com
. Please note that we may need to verify your identity and request additional information before processing your request.
How Do We Handle Children’s Information?
Our Services are not intended for or directed to children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect or solicit any information from anyone under the age of 13. If you are under 13, please do not use our Services or provide us with any information. If we learn that we have collected or received information from a child under 13, we will delete that information as soon as possible. If you believe that we might have any information from or about a child under 13, please contact us at
info@easyfastapp.com
.
How Do We Update This Privacy Policy?
We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our Services, practices, or laws. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated privacy policy on our app and website, and by sending you an email or a notification through our Services. We encourage you to review this privacy policy periodically to stay informed about how we collect, use, and share your information. Your continued use of our Services after we post or notify you of any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated privacy policy.
